    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-10-27</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-09-19T14:07:02Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Reaching Every Homeless Veteran Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Labor, in administering homeless veterans reintegration programs, to (1) consider grant applications from entities in all states (to the maximum extent practicable), and (2) conduct an outreach and education program in states where no entity has been awarded a grant to ensure communities are aware of homeless veterans reintegration programs.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
